<div class="jumbotron">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Tracks</h1>
        <p>Accept a music genre type as input and do the following:</p>
        <p>1. Pick a random artist associated to that genre from “ genres.json ” file, which will be
provided by us.</p>
        <p>2. Filter the most popular 5 tracks (songs) of that artist by using Spotify Web API (eg.
“rock” genre will retrieve the most popular 5 track info of randomly chosen artist “Led
Zeppelin”).</p>
    </div>
</div>
<form action="/" method="post" role="form" enctype="application/x-www-form-urlencoded">
    <legend>Spotify Query</legend>

    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="param_type">Genre</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" name="param_genre" id="param_genre" placeholder="rock">
    </div>

    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
</form>
{{#if results}}
    <table class="table table-striped table-hover">
        <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>Artist</th>
            <th>Track</th>
            <th>Album image url</th>
            <th>Release date</th>
        </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
        {{#each results}}
            <tr>
                <td>{{artist}}</td>
                <td>{{track}}</td>
                <td><img src="{{album_image_url}}" alt="{{album_image_url}}"></td>
                <td>{{release_date}}</td>
            </tr>
        {{/each}}
        </tbody>
    </table>
{{/if}}
{{#if errors}}
    <h1>{{errors}}</h1>
{{/if}}